articles.title: API shows U.S. crude stocks fall -market sources - Reuters.com
articles.description: U.S. crude oil stockpiles fell in the latest week, while fuel stockpiles rose, according to market sources citing American Petroleum Institute figures on Tuesday.
articles.content:
NEW YORK, Nov 15 (Reuters) - U.S. crude oil stockpiles fell in the latest week, while fuel stockpiles rose, according to market sources citing American Petroleum Institute figures on Tuesday.
